---
title: Cajun-Spiced Chicken Burger with DIY Dill Mayo
description: We're un-Cajun the beast of great taste tonight! Terrible puns aside, this spicy Southern-style crispy chicken will set your taste buds on fire. Good thing you've also got some delectable dill mayo to cool things off.
